'''圣托马斯教堂'''（{{lang-en|St Thomas' Church}}）是一座位于[[英国|英国]][[大曼彻斯特郡|大曼彻斯特郡]][[斯托克波特|斯托克波特]][[圣托马斯广场|圣托马斯广场]]的{{Link-en|英格蘭教會堂區教堂|Church of England parish church}}，是一座I级[[登录建筑|登录建筑]]。<ref>{{Citation| url = http://www.achurchnearyou.com/stockport-st-thomas1825/| title = St Thomas, Stockport| accessdate = 14 December 2011| publisher = [[英國國教會|英國國教會]]| archive-date = 2016-08-28| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160828135337/https://www.achurchnearyou.com/stockport-st-thomas1825/| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="nhl">{{NHLE |num= 1067160|desc= Parish Church of St Thomas, Stockport|accessdate= 14 December 2011|mode=cs2|ps=none}}</ref><ref name="port">{{Citation | last = Port| first = M. H.| author-link = | publication-date = | date = | year = 2006| title = 600 New Churches: The Church Building Commission 1818-1856 | edition = 2nd| volume = | series = | publication-place = Reading| place = | publisher = Spire Books| pages = | page = 326| isbn = 978-1-904965-08-4}}</ref>教堂于1822年开始建造，于1825年建成，由George Basevii设计，是他的早期作品之一。

圣托马斯教堂是一座希腊复兴式建筑。

